OL,3,CElderly woman dies after fall from
OL,4,Ccare home window
OL,6,FAn elderly woman has died after
OL,7,Ffalling from a care home window.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called out to
OL,10,FBerrycroft Manor care home in Romiley,
OL,11,FStockport, at around 7.30am on Monday
OL,12,FSeptember 29.
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) says a
OL,15,F78-year-old woman was taken to
OL,16,Fhospital following a fall, where she
OL,17,Fsadly died later that day.
