OL,6,FBerrycroft Manor's manager described
OL,7,Fthe incident as a "tragic accident"
OL,8,Fand confirmed an investigation was
OL,9,Funderway.
OL,11,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC), the
OL,12,Fregulator for care homes and medical
OL,13,Fproviders, is aware of the incident.
OL,15,FMichael Blissett, home manager at
OL,16,FBerrycroft Manor, said: "This was a
OL,17,Ftragic accident, and our thoughts and
OL,18,Fprayers are very much with the family.
OL,19,FWe extend our heartfelt condolences to
OL,20,Fthem.
