OL,6,F"Everyone here is shocked and saddened
OL,7,Fby the accident. Investigations are
OL,8,Fstill continuing as to exactly how
OL,9,Fthis has happened.
OL,11,F"Safety here is paramount and we are
OL,12,Fworking with HSE (Health and Safety
OL,13,FExecutive) and CQC to ensure this
OL,14,Fnever happens again."
OL,16,FA GMP spokesperson added: "Shortly
OL,17,Fafter 7.30am yesterday (September 29),
OL,18,Fofficers responded to reports of a
OL,19,Fconcern for the welfare of a woman
OL,20,Ffollowing a fall at a care home on
OL,21,FBerrycroft Lane, Stockport.
