OL,6,F"Emergency services attended but
OL,7,Fsadly, a 78-year-old woman died from
OL,8,Fher injuries in hospital later that
OL,9,Fday.
OL,11,F"Her family are currently being
OL,12,Fsupported. Enquiries are ongoing to
OL,13,Festablish the full circumstances of
OL,14,Fher death."
OL,16,FThe CQC last inspected the care home
OL,17,Fin September 2024, when it gave the
OL,18,Fhome a rating of 'good'.
