OL,6,FThe regulator says it has spoken to
OL,7,FBerrycroft Manor and GMP about the
OL,8,Fincident.
OL,10,FA CQC spokesperson said: "CQC has been
OL,11,Fmade aware of the death of a resident
OL,12,Fat Berrycroft Manor in Stockport, and
OL,13,Four condolences are with the family at
OL,14,Fthis sad time.
OL,16,F"We are in close contact with the home
OL,17,Fand police as they look into the
OL,18,Fcircumstances around this incident, so
OL,19,Fwe can understand if there is any
OL,20,Fregulatory action that needs taken to
OL,21,Fensure people are receiving safe care.
